WEBVTT

00:01:59.690 --> 00:02:02.995
Childhood stories might be the best memories
we have of the war!

00:02:03.118 --> 00:02:08.303
Should I forget everything
I learned in Arabic, just to conform?

00:02:08.423 --> 00:02:11.588
To be one of them?

00:02:11.878 --> 00:02:14.022
Where's the logic in that?

00:02:14.132 --> 00:02:17.690
Despite all that,
I tried to understand him.

00:02:17.780 --> 00:02:23.946
I didn't want to judge him
with the same cruelty that he judged me.

00:02:23.946 --> 00:02:27.712
The Arabic language
doesn't satisfy today's needs.

00:02:27.902 --> 00:02:29.694
It's not a language for science,

00:02:29.764 --> 00:02:31.215
research,